locations: SAE Melbourne - 235 Normanby Road, South Melbourne, Victoria, Australia
imdb.plot outline: Take a dash of Drunk History, a splash of Danger 5, a healthy dollop of Fan-Fiction, stir it all up and what do you get? Fan(tastic) Fiction. An anthology style, satirical web comedy. We have scoured the ends of the earth, well that's a lie, we did a quick google search and collected some of the most illiterate, nonsensical, mind-numbing, and occasionally incredibly offensive fan fiction that's ever been produced. We then decided we would take these literary treasures and produce short films based exactly on what has been written. Get ready to delve into a world of Space-fairing Ponlys (ponies), ultra-violent idiotic Batmen, and sexually charged romances between Edward Cullen and the legendary Dracula.
